data.description: LOADS OF IMPROVEMENTS in this adorable ranch!3 bedroom on a full walkout basement with possible 4th bedroom/office below. Large den, could be used as a theater room, in the basement with fireplace; great for fall weather.  Possible 2nd bath in the basement.  HUGE custom garage, that is 23.5 feet deep, with work bench, loft, its own electrical panel, and overhead lighting with built in bluetooth speakers. Upstairs has hardwood floors, plenty of closet space, and a rebuilt deck off the kitchen. Laundry hookups on both floors with a laundry shoot! New metal roof, shutters, and newer windows.  HVAC installed in 2018 and new sump pump.  Come make this YOUR home!
